title: Thirty Seconds to Mars - Artifact (film)
description:
The original Artifact movie, about Thirty Seconds to Mars lawsuit in between A Beautiful Lie and This Is War.

Directed by Jared Leto, and winner of several awards.

DISCLAIMER

Jared himself would not like this product shared freely, he charged $15 for this. But I believe some people may be able to appreciate it. The band has fans all over the world, and some in poor countries, I would like to see this spread out. This movie has a message that all people need to learn. For this reason I decided to "betray" (in a way) Jared and the entire band. Because I believe that:

1- This movie should be watched by everyone
2- This movie should've been shipped and showed in cinemas

I know the band needs money to support itself, but a lot of people are not able to pay for the price in dollars. Most third world countries (which are the largest pirate population) are unable to pay through internet, and even if they could, it's a lot of money due to exchange. I've experienced it myself, and I'd rather be "the bad guy" in Jared's eyes than to have this movie never be shared by anyone and stay only to a few thousand people who were able to pay it.

I do not own this property and just share it with the world! I'm not a criminal, I'm just sharing :)

Now that this issue has been dealt, hope you enjoy the movie. :)
